<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include("partials/head") %>
    <meta name="description" content="Get help using LNC Research Archives - FAQs, guides, and troubleshooting tips." />
    <title>Help - LNC Research Archives</title>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/notifications.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="bg-bokeh"></div>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <main class="container">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="card highlight">
        <h1>❓ Help Center</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Find answers to common questions, learn how to use the platform, and get the support
          you need.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>📋 Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="stack" style="gap: 20px; margin-top: 12px;">

          <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--primary); padding-left: 16px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">How do I create an account?</h4>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">Click <strong>"Request Account"</strong> in the navigation bar. Fill in
              your details and wait for an administrator to approve your request. You'll receive an email once your
              account is ready.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 16px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">How do I upload a thesis?</h4>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">After logging in as a <strong>Student</strong>, click <strong>"Upload
                Thesis"</strong> in the navbar. Fill in all required fields including title, abstract, course, and
              upload your document file.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--success); padding-left: 16px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">How does the review process work?</h4>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">Once a thesis is submitted, it enters a <strong>Pending</strong> state.
              Advisers and designated reviewers can then evaluate the work. After approval, the thesis becomes publicly
              visible in the repository.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--warning); padding-left: 16px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Can I edit my thesis after submission?</h4>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">No. But you can edit your thesis if the thesis is still in <strong>Pending</strong> status, you
              can edit its details. Once it has been approved, you cannot edit it anymore.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--danger); padding-left: 16px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">I forgot my password. What should I do?</h4>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">For faster process, please contact the designated administrator in your institution to have your
              password reset.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-light); padding-left: 16px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">How do I get a copy of a thesis?</h4>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">Click the <strong>"Request Thesis via Email"</strong> button on any approved thesis page. Provide a reason for your request (minimum 20 characters). The author and administrator will be notified and, once either approves, the PDF will be sent directly to your registered email address.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- User Roles Guide -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🎭 User Roles</h2>
        <p class="muted">The platform supports three roles, each with different permissions:</p>
        <div class="grid" style="margin-top: 16px;">
          <div class="card" style="border-color: var(--primary);">
            <h3 style="color: var(--primary-light);">🎓 Student</h3>
            <ul
              style="color: var(--muted); list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
              <li>✅ Upload/Edit pending thesis</li>
              <li>✅ Request thesis files via email</li>
              <li>✅ View all approved thesis</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="border-color: var(--accent);">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-light);">👨‍🏫 Teacher</h3>
            <ul
              style="color: var(--muted); list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
              <li>✅ Approve/revoke advised thesis</li>
              <li>✅ Access pending thesis queue</li>
              <li>✅ View all thesis</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="border-color: var(--warning);">
            <h3 style="color: var(--warning-light);">⚙️ Admin</h3>
            <ul
              style="color: var(--muted); list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
              <li>✅ Manage all users & roles</li>
              <li>✅ Approve account requests</li>
              <li>✅ View dashboard & reports</li>
              <li>✅ Full platform control</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Still Need Help -->
      <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h2>💬 Still Need Help?</h2>
        <p class="muted">If you can't find the answer you're looking for, don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn" style="margin-top: 8px;">📧 Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>